<br>
Those of us there, all four of us that randomed didn't agree with the GM forcing us to random, and we all requested the petitions to be escalated to a lead or supervisor and never got a response... So we petitioned again, got another guide and not what any of requested, who did nothing... Essentially told us we should all group together and kill FGs, we're all wondering what the heck this has to do with the problem... He briefly said something about talking to an actual GM on our behalf and see about doing something about this spawn, then he kept going LD and last time he never returned... Nothing got resolved, again people petitioned again and for the rest of the day, evening, and through the middle of the night no other response to the situation was given... That means this server, the people here, HAVE to do something... There's going to be sooooo much dispute down there and hatred over silly friggen gankings of it by those that can't respect other clerics there longer than themselves... <br>
<br>
As Dornie said something should be done so it doesn't turn into a melting pot of nastiness down there, and folks I know firsthand that's exactly what is going to happen... <br>
<br>
In closing I was there a day and a half, I was 20 minutes behind Cephas who got the camp before me... I arrived 20 minutes after him to claim for next spawn and everyone was told that... Essentially I'm feeling very much disillusioned at this server's community, and disrespect for a particular cleric... I'm tired, grouchy, and just not a happy person right now... <br>
<br>
Edit: This is something I also come to realize and decided I had an opinion on... Stats, 15 people on the old RF list have swapped pearls... 15 blasted people out of a list of 76... I'd really like to know those within the top 10 or top 20 hadn't already done this... They were lazy, I was in the 60s and knew I was in for over a year wait, this is/was my excuse... Now I severely regret it... I could have my epic right now had I swapped my pearl, and yes at the moment I am bitter... Every SINGLE person towards the bottom/top however you look at it of the list, should have already swapped their pearls... This bottleneck wouldn't be so friggen bad here if you guys had done as you were supposed to... <br>
