<br>
This is a bottleneck, but no where near as bad as RF was. I am greatful for the change and I can wait another month or two before I see my epic. I've seen some of my very best friends get their epics this week. It's a wonderful thing. I saw people helping each other in Skyfire, strangers helping others. Clerics that have waited months getting thier epics, it's great!<br>
<br>
